The reference for the paper cited above is:
Work TM, Russell R, Aeby GS: Tissue loss (white syndrome) in the coral _Montipora capitata_ is a dynamic disease with multiple host responses and potential causes. Proc Biol Sci. 2012 Nov 7; 279(1746): 4334-41. Epub 2012 Sep 5; available at http://rspb.royalsocietypublishing.org/content/279/1746/4334.long. - Sr.Tech.Ed.MJ]
